text.section:
The Board shall renew the license of an occupational therapist or an occupational therapy assistant who has failed to renew the license for any reason if the occupational therapist or occupational therapy assistant:
Applies for renewal within 30 days after the deadline for renewal;
Meets the renewal requirements of this section;
Pays to the Board the renewal fee set by the Board; and
Pays to the Board the late fee set by the Board.
